<% layout("../layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/host-resources.css">

<div class="info-page">
    <div class="info-container">

        <div class="page-header">
            <i class="bi bi-journal-bookmark-fill"></i>
            <h1>Host Resources</h1>
            <p>
                Helpful resources, best practices, and tools to help you
                succeed as a VibeStay host.
            </p>
        </div>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-house-check"></i>
                Creating a Great Listing
            </h2>
            <p>
                Your listing is the first thing guests see. A complete,
                detailed, and attractive listing increases visibility
                and booking requests.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Upload high-quality photos.</li>
                <li>Write clear and accurate descriptions.</li>
                <li>Highlight unique features and amenities.</li>
                <li>Keep pricing competitive.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i>
                Booking Management
            </h2>
            <p>
                Review booking requests regularly and respond quickly.
                Fast response times improve guest confidence and increase
                successful reservations.
            </p>

            <div class="resource-card">
                <i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill"></i>
                <span>Quick responses often lead to better guest satisfaction.</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                Getting Better Reviews
            </h2>
            <p>
                Positive reviews help build trust and improve your property's
                visibility on the platform.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Maintain cleanliness.</li>
                <li>Provide accurate property details.</li>
                <li>Communicate clearly with guests.</li>
                <li>Offer a smooth check-in experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-cash-stack"></i>
                Pricing Strategy
            </h2>
            <p>
                Smart pricing helps maximize occupancy and revenue.
                Adjust prices based on demand, seasons, holidays,
                and local events.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                Safety & Security
            </h2>
            <p>
                Create a safe and comfortable environment for guests by
                maintaining your property and following local regulations.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li>Keep emergency contacts available.</li>
                <li>Ensure property information is accurate.</li>
                <li>Maintain secure access systems.</li>
                <li>Inspect rooms regularly.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="info-section">
            <h2>
                <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
                Growing Your Hosting Business
            </h2>
            <p>
                Consistent service quality, strong reviews, and excellent
                guest experiences can help increase bookings and grow
                your hosting success over time.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>